  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2eba04e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FpkWC42uvwkmN24ic1edsuJZ3nZyicOvFlIj6ycewibuwWM6WFoHVibx0bnN7TZAeUYHLYauWfLg6biaNpjmIQDN3agw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DeepSeek-V3.1 现已更新至 DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus 版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此次更新在保持模型原有能力的基础上，针对用户反馈的问题进行了改进，包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">语言一致性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">缓解了中英文混杂、偶发异常字符等情况</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Agent 能力</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：进一步优化了 Code Agent 与 Search Agent 的表现。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;UqcZdX67xov5tcxKskccAuAQnSf&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;此次更新在保持模型原有能力的基础上，重点优化了Code Agent与Search Agent的表现，并针对用户反馈的问题进行了修复：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1u&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7273692048102965249&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;ac382502-ec92-4538-92f1-343055421c31&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:4,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:66},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;WwCQd22LooQXFRxgP1JcgcLmnce&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"></ul>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus 的输出效果相比前一版本更加稳定，新模型各领域测评结果如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/pkWC42uvwkmN24ic1edsuJZ3nZyicOvFlIAPYHzkRwZTt3HkDH5ibDExQICnugA3qUXyeE0DAU5fSEkGqiaVZwxTAg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy2=\"1227.9715302491104\" data-imgfileid=\"100001999\" data-ratio=\"1.137037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:562px;height:639px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f89e43b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FpkWC42uvwkmN24ic1edsuJZ3nZyicOvFlIk6dCcgmmbKWV7uYs9dkXdWH0N2zVNOQARw8lz9lLltGGIxNY2PKVUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;UqcZdX67xov5tcxKskccAuAQnSf&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;修复更新后，模型的输出效果更加稳定可靠。模型测评结果如下：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+m*1+7&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7313741941510488068&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7273692048102965249&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;46597df9-f027-464b-b427-136b4df6a407&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:9,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:29},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;EFCQdlUTzo9V6ixOg6acIptcnhf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">注：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Search Agent 的工具集与上一版有所不同，具体工具细节请查看 HuggingFace 文档</span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;UqcZdX67xov5tcxKskccAuAQnSf&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;注：Search Agent 的工具集与上一版有小幅度变化，更新为search, open, find三个工具&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1j&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7273692048102965249&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;91e2f682-5590-442b-a9a2-8fbf2f23d111&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:57,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:55},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;GMtOdXKROoXU12xmIuScwptgnzb&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，官方 App、网页端、小程序与 DeepSeek API 模型</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">均已</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同步</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更新为 DeepSeek-</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">V</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3.1-Terminus。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源版本下载地址如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;UqcZdX67xov5tcxKskccAuAQnSf&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;开源版本下载地址如下：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+b&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7313741941510488068&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;c7426a1b-11ce-4b4f-bc0e-e306dbb8dc1e&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:60,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:11},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;EDcFdFA1UolhKjxk1n6c3hEYneg&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Hugging Face：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(77, 107, 254);\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">ModelScope：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(77, 107, 254);\"><a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">感谢并欢迎广大用户积极反馈在使用 DeepSeek 模型过程中遇到的各类问题，我们将持续迭代提升模型性能，优化用户使用体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001992\" data-ratio=\"0.5890625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abe2cb4b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FpkWC42uvwkkzHicnc3yYQtiaReJIG84YPl7XRAYlia89diatyex4jjq8n90q9ViajyVBcqxsAkXhpDiaFg9vM2kzg9cA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepSeek-V3.1 模型更新至 Terminus 版本，重点提升了语言一致性和 Code/Search Agent 能力，并已同步上线及开源。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepSeek-V3.1 模型更新至 Terminus 版本，重点提升了语言一致性和 Code/Search Agent 能力，并已同步上线及开源。",
  "summary": "文章发布了 DeepSeek-V3.1 模型的重要更新，现已升级至 DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus 版本。此次更新主要针对用户反馈，着重改进了模型的语言一致性，有效缓解了中英文混杂和偶发异常字符等问题。同时，Code Agent 和 Search Agent 的能力也得到了进一步优化，新版本宣称输出效果更加稳定。文章附带了一张模型在各领域测评结果的截图。DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus 已全面同步至官方 App、网页端、小程序、DeepSeek API，并提供了 HuggingFace 和 ModelScope 的开源下载地址，鼓励用户积极反馈以持续提升模型性能。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-V3.1-Terminus 版本显著提升了语言一致性",
      "explanation": "新模型有效解决了中英文混杂及异常字符问题，使得模型输出更加稳定、规范，提升了用户体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Code Agent 与 Search Agent 能力获得进一步优化",
      "explanation": "此次更新增强了模型在代码生成和信息检索方面的表现，拓宽了其在开发和知识获取领域的应用潜力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
